member.name: HTTPAPI_VERSION
member.summary: TheHTTPAPI_VERSION structure defines the version of the HTTP Server API. This is not to be confused with the version of the HTTP protocol used, which is stored in anHTTP_VERSION structure.

member.summary: Major version of the HTTP Server API.
